Package com.asemantics.inspector

Interface Summary
InspectorParser Responsible to parse an expression.
 

Class Summary
BeanAccessor Utility class to handle bean properties.
Inspector Represents a bean inspector able to process inspection strings.
InspectorParserImpl Default implementation of InspectorParser.
ListReaderPattern Pattern to read an enumerable (ordered) type: Array Collection List
Pattern format: <attribute_name>[<index>]
Pattern Describes an inspection atomic operation.
PropertyReaderPattern Pattern to read a bean attrivute: property method
Pattern format: <attribute_name>
 

Exception Summary
InspectorParserException Defines an exception occurring while inspecting a bean graph.
PatternException Describes an exception raised while parsing a pattern expression.
